Nigerian comedians, Basketmouth, Chigurl, Ushebebe, IK Osakioduwa, on Thursday, paid a surprise visit To Big Brother Naija Housemates. The entertainers visited the house to interact with housemates and also judge their comic play. Housemates were tasked to prepare a comic play for their final task presentation. Recall that Nollywood stars, Patience Ozorkwo, AKA Mama G, Chinedu Ikedieze, Maiatafo, Osas Ighodaro, Akande Dakore, Mr Ibu and Lala Akindoju on Wednesday visited housemates in the Big Brother Naija, BBNaija, reality show. The actors during their visit, advised housemates on how to use the platform wisely. Biggie also surprised housemates with dinner after welcoming the superstars. The housemates, who expressed excitement during the visit, were advised to show good character, be committed in their work and give back to the society. See video   The Guess are here wow a full arena with great comedic A post shared by  Blog_world1 (@bigbrothernaijapage) on Sep 26, 2019 at 1:16pm PDT  Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.